data.description: *LISTED AT APPRAISED VALUE* Welcome to your dream home nestled on a generous 1.29-acre lot with breathtaking sunset views in a tranquil country setting. This charming residence boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,426 sqft of comfortable living space.  As you approach, you'll be captivated by the curb appeal of this delightful abode with its classic brick front and warm wood siding. The 2-car attached garage provides both convenience and storage space.  Step inside to discover a host of modern updates and features. The home welcomes you with a sense of elegance and comfort, thanks to new appliances and stylish updates throughout. The bathrooms have been tastefully upgraded to provide both luxury and convenience.  The spacious living areas showcase brand new Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring, creating a seamless flow from room to room. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening by the fireplace, this home offers the perfect backdrop for making cherished memories.  Outside, the expansive yard offers endless possibilities, from gardening to outdoor activities, all while enjoying the picturesque countryside. This property truly provides the best of both worlds: the tranquility of country living and the convenience of modern amenities.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated and well-maintained home yours. Schedule a viewing today and experience the charm of country living with all the comforts of modern living.
